Siamspinops formosensis

from Taipei, Taiwan. 1–5 female, TESRI-Ar1902 (1 dorsal view of cephalothorax and abdomen, 2 retrolateral view of left leg I, 3 ventral view of left chelicera, 4 ventral view of epigyne, 5 dorsal view of vulva); 6–10, male, TESRI-Ar1903 (6 dorsal view of cephalothorax and abdomen, 7 retrolateral view of left leg II, 8 ventral view of left chelicera, 9 ventral view of left palp, 10 retrolateral view of left palp). Scales: 1mm. 
